                            <title>Unidentified protective prayer against the men’s tongue</title>
                            <note>The text is for the most part illegible due to faded ink.
                                The following text is partially legible on  <locus target="#3r"/>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ልሳነ፡ ሰብ<gap reason="lost"/></foreign>.
                            </note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="11r" to="23v"/>
                            <title ref="LIT5690MagicPrayer"/>
                            <note>The text is for the most part illegible due to faded ink. The identification is tentative and is based on the following portion of text which is readable on
                                <locus target="#11v"/>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እንዘ፡ ይሐውር፡ እግዚእነ፡ ውስተ፡ ባሕረ፡ ጥብርያዶስ፡  ወምስሌሁ፡ ፲ወ፪ አርዳኢሁ፡ ርእዩ፡ መልክአ፡ ብእሲት፡ አረጊት፡</foreign>.
                            </note>
                        </msItem>
